      "writtenOn": "2017-10-17T20:10:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "For simplicity: not having to keep a lot of implicit state in our heads while editing this, can we minimize the number of translations/detranslations that happen? Maybe we keep both the original and translated name in the uniform desc struct.",
